Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.87,0:16:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2}地球形成的原理似乎非常简单\N{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2\fnSegoe UI\b0\fscx66\fscy66\fsp0\c&HFAFAFA&\3c&H101010&\3a&HFF&\4c&H000000&\4a&H50&)}There seems to be nothing subtle about the way earth was built.
