Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.73,0:16:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2}我们骨骼中的钙 婚戒中的金\N{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2\fnSegoe UI\b0\fscx66\fscy66\fsp0\c&HFAFAFA&\3c&H101010&\3a&HFF&\4c&H000000&\4a&H50&)}The calcium in our bones, the gold in our wedding rings,
