Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.33,0:17:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2}是他们渴望的工作\N{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2\fnSegoe UI\b0\fscx66\fscy66\fsp0\c&HFAFAFA&\3c&H101010&\3a&HFF&\4c&H000000&\4a&H50&)}that they wanted to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.81,0:17:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2}对我来说 不是这么回事\N{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2\fnSegoe UI\b0\fscx66\fscy66\fsp0\c&HFAFAFA&\3c&H101010&\3a&HFF&\4c&H000000&\4a&H50&)}For me, it wasn't that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.88,0:17:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2}我的背景是航空工程\N{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2\fnSegoe UI\b0\fscx66\fscy66\fsp0\c&HFAFAFA&\3c&H101010&\3a&HFF&\4c&H000000&\4a&H50&)}My background is aeronautical engineering.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.29,0:17:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2}我渴望做与飞行相关的事\N{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2\fnSegoe UI\b0\fscx66\fscy66\fsp0\c&HFAFAFA&\3c&H101010&\3a&HFF&\4c&H000000&\4a&H50&)}I wanted to do something with flying
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.83,0:17:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2}可以让我学到事物升空的原理\N{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2\fnSegoe UI\b0\fscx66\fscy66\fsp0\c&HFAFAFA&\3c&H101010&\3a&HFF&\4c&H000000&\4a&H50&)}that allowed me to learn about how things fly
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.70,0:17:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2}如果你想了解事物是如何飞上天的\N{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2\fnSegoe UI\b0\fscx66\fscy66\fsp0\c&HFAFAFA&\3c&H101010&\3a&HFF&\4c&H000000&\4a&H50&)}and then ultimately if you wanna know how things fly,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.60,0:17:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2}就不可能不想知道火箭是如何起飞的\N{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2\fnSegoe UI\b0\fscx66\fscy66\fsp0\c&HFAFAFA&\3c&H101010&\3a&HFF&\4c&H000000&\4a&H50&)}I can't imagine not wanting to know how rocket ships fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:17:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2}于是某天有人打电话给我说\N{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2\fnSegoe UI\b0\fscx66\fscy66\fsp0\c&HFAFAFA&\3c&H101010&\3a&HFF&\4c&H000000&\4a&H50&)}And then one day I got this phone call
