Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.16,0:18:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2}进行一次长期飞行作业\N{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2\fnSegoe UI\b0\fscx66\fscy66\fsp0\c&HFAFAFA&\3c&H101010&\3a&HFF&\4c&H000000&\4a&H50&)}on the International Space Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.78,0:18:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2}妮可原本不打算上空间站\N{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2\fnSegoe UI\b0\fscx66\fscy66\fsp0\c&HFAFAFA&\3c&H101010&\3a&HFF&\4c&H000000&\4a&H50&)}Nicole didn't set out to fly on the ISS,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.20,0:18:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2}她是空间站的建造师\N{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2\fnSegoe UI\b0\fscx66\fscy66\fsp0\c&HFAFAFA&\3c&H101010&\3a&HFF&\4c&H000000&\4a&H50&)}her job was to build the thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.43,0:18:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2}即便她上到了太空中 满脑子也都是设计 \N{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2\fnSegoe UI\b0\fscx66\fscy66\fsp0\c&HFAFAFA&\3c&H101010&\3a&HFF&\4c&H000000&\4a&H50&)}but once she got up there, she still had an eye for design.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2}所以身为一名工程师\N{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2\fnSegoe UI\b0\fscx66\fscy66\fsp0\c&HFAFAFA&\3c&H101010&\3a&HFF&\4c&H000000&\4a&H50&)}So as an engineer you can imagine,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.76,0:18:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2}在我看向地球时 不得不好奇\N{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2\fnSegoe UI\b0\fscx66\fscy66\fsp0\c&HFAFAFA&\3c&H101010&\3a&HFF&\4c&H000000&\4a&H50&)}I couldn't help but look at the earth and wonder,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.69,0:18:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2}它是怎么运转的\N{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2\fnSegoe UI\b0\fscx66\fscy66\fsp0\c&HFAFAFA&\3c&H101010&\3a&HFF&\4c&H000000&\4a&H50&)}how does that work?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.43,0:18:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2}望向地球时 有一点显而易见\N{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2\fnSegoe UI\b0\fscx66\fscy66\fsp0\c&HFAFAFA&\3c&H101010&\3a&HFF&\4c&H000000&\4a&H50&)}What's blindingly obvious when you look at earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2}水是关键\N{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2\fnSegoe UI\b0\fscx66\fscy66\fsp0\c&HFAFAFA&\3c&H101010&\3a&HFF&\4c&H000000&\4a&H50&)}is water is the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.87,0:19:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2}但早期的地球 并不是我如今所见的蓝色星球\N{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2\fnSegoe UI\b0\fscx66\fscy66\fsp0\c&HFAFAFA&\3c&H101010&\3a&HFF&\4c&H000000&\4a&H50&)}But earlier it didn't look like this blue planet that I saw,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2}那是一块干燥荒芜的巨石\N{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2\fnSegoe UI\b0\fscx66\fscy66\fsp0\c&HFAFAFA&\3c&H101010&\3a&HFF&\4c&H000000&\4a&H50&)} it was a dry and barren rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2}为了生命的兴盛\N{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2\fnSegoe UI\b0\fscx66\fscy66\fsp0\c&HFAFAFA&\3c&H101010&\3a&HFF&\4c&H000000&\4a&H50&)}For life to thrive like it has done,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.15,0:19:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2}地球需要外界的水源\N{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2\fnSegoe UI\b0\fscx66\fscy66\fsp0\c&HFAFAFA&\3c&H101010&\3a&HFF&\4c&H000000&\4a&H50&)}the earth needed delivery of water.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.56,0:19:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2}我们认为地球成型后不久\N{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2\fnSegoe UI\b0\fscx66\fscy66\fsp0\c&HFAFAFA&\3c&H101010&\3a&HFF&\4c&H000000&\4a&H50&)}We believe soon after the earth was formed,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.52,0:19:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2}水就从外太空疯狂袭来\N{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2\fnSegoe UI\b0\fscx66\fscy66\fsp0\c&HFAFAFA&\3c&H101010&\3a&HFF&\4c&H000000&\4a&H50&)}our water came from space in a hail of violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.23,0:19:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2}那情景想必非常凶猛\N{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2\fnSegoe UI\b0\fscx66\fscy66\fsp0\c&HFAFAFA&\3c&H101010&\3a&HFF&\4c&H000000&\4a&H50&)}It must have been brutal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.35,0:19:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2}我们猜测这暴雨下了一亿年左右\N{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2\fnSegoe UI\b0\fscx66\fscy66\fsp0\c&HFAFAFA&\3c&H101010&\3a&HFF&\4c&H000000&\4a&H50&)}We think it lasted for about 100 million years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.98,0:20:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2}由冰组成的彗星和小行星再次撞向地球\N{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2\fnSegoe UI\b0\fscx66\fscy66\fsp0\c&HFAFAFA&\3c&H101010&\3a&HFF&\4c&H000000&\4a&H50&)}Icy comets and asteroids collided with the planet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.39,0:20:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2}从而给予了我们水\N{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2\fnSegoe UI\b0\fscx66\fscy66\fsp0\c&HFAFAFA&\3c&H101010&\3a&HFF&\4c&H000000&\4a&H50&)}To supply us with that top off of water.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.44,0:20:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2}然而不像同被暴雨轰炸过的火星和金星\N{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2\fnSegoe UI\b0\fscx66\fscy66\fsp0\c&HFAFAFA&\3c&H101010&\3a&HFF&\4c&H000000&\4a&H50&)}But unlike Mars and Venus, who were surely bombarded by the same storm,
