Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.58,0:21:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2}幸运的是\N{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2\fnSegoe UI\b0\fscx66\fscy66\fsp0\c&HFAFAFA&\3c&H101010&\3a&HFF&\4c&H000000&\4a&H50&)}As luck would have it,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.26,0:21:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2}造就当今地球样貌的原石\N{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2\fnSegoe UI\b0\fscx66\fscy66\fsp0\c&HFAFAFA&\3c&H101010&\3a&HFF&\4c&H000000&\4a&H50&)}the seed that would one day grow, into the earth we know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.46,0:21:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2}在距离太阳最合适的轨道上安定了下来\N{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2\fnSegoe UI\b0\fscx66\fscy66\fsp0\c&HFAFAFA&\3c&H101010&\3a&HFF&\4c&H000000&\4a&H50&)}found its place at the perfect distance from the sun,
