Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.44,0:21:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2}地球上的每一滴水 原本都很可能\N{\shad0.8\bord0.1\blur2\fnSegoe UI\b0\fscx66\fscy66\fsp0\c&HFAFAFA&\3c&H101010&\3a&HFF&\4c&H000000&\4a&H50&)}Earth could have easily wound up somewhere where every drop
